AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000112> :pmcid "   A PMCID is a unique PubMed Central reference number, which is assigned to each full-text record made available A PMCID is a unique PubMed Central reference number, which is assigned to each full-text record made available in PubMed Central. The PMCID is issued shortly after the PI or author approves the PubMed Central formatted web version of the submission. ")
