# Data Property: :sponsorAwardId (sponsor award ID)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000112> :sponsorAwardId "Has a domain of Grant. There is not a strong reason have this be publically visible, since most users would care more about the name of the sponsoring agency than its identifier, but it does no harm to be public.


