AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000003> "A measurement unit label is as a label that is part of a scalar measurement datum and denotes a unit of measure."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000116> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000003> "2009-03-16: provenance: a term measurement unit was
