# Class: <http://purl.org/ontology/bibo/DocumentStatus> (Document Status)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000112> <http://purl.org/ontology/bibo/DocumentStatus> "The status of a document with respect to its publication. The statuses are represented as individuals of this class. Use the \"show all individuals of this class\" button on the class control panel to see the currently defined statuses.")
