AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.org/ontology/bibo/Manuscript> "Works prepared by hand including handwritten or typescript drafts of pre-publication papers or works not otherwise reproduced in multiple copies")
