AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000112> <http://purl.org/ontology/bibo/Map> "The Short Definition is how the bibo ontology defines Map. It has been extended to include more broader concept of map which includes science maps, social network maps.")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.org/ontology/bibo/Map> "A graphical depiction of geographic features, scientific discipline, scientific data analytical results")
