AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000112> <http://purl.org/ontology/bibo/PersonalCommunicationDocument> "A personal communication manifested in some document.")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.org/ontology/bibo/PersonalCommunicationDocument> "A personal communication manifested in some document.")
