AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000112> :CurationProcess "Jane is curator of Collection c. Jane is a person.  Jane bearer_of curatorRole r.  r realized_in CurationProcess p.  p has_input c."@en)
