AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> :CurationProcess "A process which has as its input, a collection of material entities and/or information content entities"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000116> :CurationProcess "Under development.  The restriction applies to has input assertions.  Collections of material entities are material entities.  Collection of information content entities are information content entities."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000117> :CurationProcess "PERSON: Michael Conlon"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000119> :CurationProcess ""@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://vitro.mannlib.cornell.edu/ns/vitro/0.7#descriptionAnnot> :CurationProcess "The curation of a collection")
