EquivalentClasses(<http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#Sound> ObjectIntersectionOf(DataAllValuesFrom(<http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#sound> xsd:anyURI) DataMinCardinality(1 <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#sound>)))
SubClassOf(<http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#Sound> <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#Explanatory>)

